  .desc = A 25-round magazine of 7.7x56mm rimmed cartridges.
ent-RMCMagazineSniperL112SH = L112 squash-head magazine (7.7x56mmR)
  .desc = A 25-round magazine of 7.7x56mm rimmed squash-head cartridges.
